"always center cursor line after moving
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz
nnoremap <C-i> <C-i>zz
nnoremap <C-o> <C-o>zz
"center cursor line on search movings
nnoremap n nzzzv
nnoremap N Nzzzv

